    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-003__align-001">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-003</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">3</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 3.1 - 老子 3.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 3.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>不尚賢，使民不爭；不貴難得之貨，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Not to value and employ men of superior ability is the way to keep the people from rivalry among themselves;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-003__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-003</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 3.4 - 老子 3.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 3.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>使民不為盜；不見可欲，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>not to prize articles which are difficult to procure is the way to keep them from becoming thieves;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-003__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-003</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 3.6 - 老子 3.7</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 3.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>使民心不亂。是以聖人之治，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>not to show them what is likely to excite their desires is the way to keep their minds from disorder.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-003__align-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-003</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">4</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 3.8 - 老子 3.11</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 3.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>虛其心，實其腹，弱其志，強其骨。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Therefore the sage, in the exercise of his government, empties their minds, fills their bellies, weakens their wills, and strengthens their bones.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-003__align-005">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-003</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 3.12 - 老子 3.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 3.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>常使民無知無欲。使夫智者不敢為也。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>He constantly (tries to) keep them without knowledge and without desire, and where there are those who have knowledge, to keep them from presuming to act (on it).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
